{"tid":43061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩建國就可以救到香港，到時全部都要死啊！","createTime":"2016-12-17T08:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T04:03:15.000Z","uid":26846,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8146f50e11e1e93926b5a798dd5c9f0175f58ec6","tid":43061,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"就算聽日中共解體，建國成功，比你班人執政，我地應該會比依家慘一百倍。<br />\n<br />\n依家未執政係自己圈子已經係要清算依個，審判果個，完全唔需要道理，你地話係就係，仲惡過共產黨。<br />\n<br />\n更加唔好話民主議會，真係講句都可能會死。<br />\n<br />\n萬一黃洋達，陳雲有權，到時一定下令葉政淳班狗奴才清算所有人。<br />\n<br />\n到時班蓋世太保到處捉人，到時咩高登仔，連登仔定連頭仔都要死。<br />\n<br />\n香港起碼有700幾萬人佢地要殺，依班撚樣有權一定會做依啲野。"},{"pid":"ccf8dbf90c728ef345fb70d05f4cbbcabe862772","tid":43061,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"樓主睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"7d0f5fefe099b2d5b1070fe784a867bf6fddf14d","tid":43061,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd60aea1f461d92441549688370bc543f752a491","tid":43061,"uid":14862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"食左藥未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07114399fb1e4edf04ecd5db7d28b22873f9650a","tid":43061,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:32:02.000Z","msg":"我有講錯？"},{"pid":"ed339eae2727afd06e72943d41fa3e6f3e19acb6","tid":43061,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"你知仲講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔驚俾人追殺到天涯海角"},{"pid":"9b20fe9d0602f32f8b757397980c5cdc7d85030e","tid":43061,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"一定係佢清算人?<br />\n唔撚比我地清算佢架?"},{"pid":"7db4243183594d9ede848f3c9d85c04bb28541c6","tid":43061,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:46:46.000Z","msg"